<plot>In Chinese folklore, a deceased person's spirit returns home to pay one last visit to his family on the seventh night after his passing before leaving for the afterlife. Filmed in the Eastern cinematic tradition, Thereafter examines family ties: a Chinese family is to perform traditional rituals while coping with the life-altering week of their lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?603753</url></doc>
